snippet.title: Seafrog | Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Seafrog is coming to Steam on April 15th, 2025! Wishlist and purchase the game on Steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2107540/Seafrog/

Master Seafrog's rocket-powered wrench as you slide, grind and trick your way through challenging skatepark-like stages at sea! Upgrade your wrench, take on crusty creatures and crazy challenges, all while seeking a way to escape a mysterious, ever-growing sinkhole in the ocean...
